activities.description: First swim of the year for Gisi and me, went at around 14:00 almost had the whole double-lane to ourselves, sun shining, very nice

Susanne had some [Fitness Mix music](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mL40wGiWbCo) for the first time which was pretty good, I found it and downloaded it onto my stick for my runs, it has intervals of 30 seconds work, 15 seconds rest.
